name: Space Rescue (ostrichstudio)
description:
physics based casual game. 78.5% people can't finish all level ! ( just kidding! haha)

if you like the game or any idea , suggestion would be appreciate.
please leave a common below!

HowToPlay

W : Main Power
A : Left Power
D : Right Power
J : Open The Door
K : Save 
R : Undo

* notice: the ship only can save when it landing properly. and need to be vertical for open the door. 

Have Fun!
